_sText:
An edited and improved version of bhop_blend. Theres not much difference in the gameplay on this version as the old one, so the map plays very closely to the classic version. I thought i could remake it since it had a few areas that were a bit imbalanced. I then took it to further level and edited the whole map because why not. 

Since the gameplay is nearly the same in both version, please remove bhop_blend and add this one to your server instead. 

Hope you enjoy! :o)
